---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-ink text-white border-t-2 border-ink">
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 divide-y-2 md:divide-y-0 md:divide-x-2 divide-white/10">

    <!-- Brand -->
    <div class="md:col-span-2 px-8 md:px-14 py-10 flex flex-col justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <a href="/" class="font-mono font-bold text-xl tracking-tight text-white">
          ■ buildify.bg
        </a>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/40 leading-relaxed max-w-xs">
          Уебсайтове, плъгини и AI ботове за малкия бизнес в България. Бургас, 2026.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="font-mono text-xs text-white/20 uppercase tracking-widest">
        Богдан Димитров · 7+ год. опит
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Услуги -->
    <div class="px-8 py-10">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/25 mb-5">Услуги</p>
      <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-sm">
        <li><a href="/websites"  class="text-white/50 hover:text-yellow transition-colors">Уебсайтове</a></li>
        <li><a href="/plugini"   class="text-white/50 hover:text-yellow transition-colors">Плъгини</a></li>
        <li><a href="/ai-botove" class="text-white/50 hover:text-yellow transition-colors">AI ботове</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Компания -->
    <div class="px-8 py-10">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/25 mb-5">Навигация</p>
      <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-sm">
        <li><a href="/blog"    class="text-white/50 hover:text-yellow transition-colors">Блог</a></li>
        <li><a href="/kontakt" class="text-white/50 hover:text-yellow transition-colors">Контакти</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- Bottom -->
  <div class="border-t border-white/10 px-8 md:px-14 py-5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3">
    <span class="font-mono text-xs text-white/20">© {year} buildify.bg — Всички права запазени</span>
    <span class="font-mono text-xs text-white/20">Astro · Cloudflare · Бургас, България</span>
  </div>
</footer>
